data.description: Lovely remodeled home with garage converted fully into an additional room added heating/cooling. With newly installed sliding door access to the backyard. Designer grey color scheme and all updated flooring.  Upgraded items include: pitched roof, windows, carpet, paint, upgraded kitchen including granite and 150 amp electric service, interior lighting, 2 evaporative cooling units, and 2 wall heaters. Also added new car port on concrete slab inside private backyard for all of your toys! Workshop/shed! Don't miss out on this one! Home is being sold AS IS seller will not make any repairs. Schedule your showing today!
